%% ModelMesh Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.24/modelmesh.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant API as ModelMesh gRPC API<br/>8033/TCP TLS
    participant Engine as SidecarModelMesh<br/>Core Engine
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP TLS
    participant LocalRT as Local Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP plaintext
    participant RemoteMM as Remote ModelMesh Pod<br/>8080/TCP TLS (Litelinks)
    participant RemoteRT as Remote Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP plaintext
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC)

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>API: gRPC Inference Request<br/>mm-model-id header<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Engine: Route request
    Engine->>etcd: Lookup model location<br/>gRPC/TLS + Certificate auth

    alt Model loaded locally
        Engine->>LocalRT: gRPC inference<br/>plaintext (localhost/UDS)
        LocalRT-->>Engine: Prediction result
    else Model on remote pod
        Engine->>RemoteMM: Forward request<br/>gRPC Litelinks/TLS<br/>Certificate auth
        RemoteMM->>RemoteRT: gRPC inference<br/>plaintext (localhost/UDS)
        RemoteRT-->>RemoteMM: Prediction result
        RemoteMM-->>Engine: Response
    end

    Engine-->>API: Inference result
    API-->>Client: gRPC Response<br/>TLS

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 2: Model Registration and Loading

    Client->>API: registerModel RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Engine: Register model
    Engine->>etcd: Store model record<br/>gRPC/TLS + Certificate
    Engine->>LocalRT: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC plaintext
    LocalRT->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/TLS + Storage creds
    Storage-->>LocalRT: Model artifacts
    LocalRT-->>Engine: Load complete (model size)
    Engine->>etcd: Update model status → LOADED
    Engine-->>API: Registration result
    API-->>Client: Model registered

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 3: Auto-Scaling (Copy Scaling)

    Engine->>etcd: Monitor request rates<br/>& instance records
    etcd-->>Engine: Current load data
    Engine->>RemoteMM: Trigger model load<br/>on target pod<br/>gRPC Litelinks/TLS
    RemoteMM->>RemoteRT: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC plaintext
    RemoteRT->>Storage: Download model<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    Storage-->>RemoteRT: Model artifacts
    RemoteRT-->>RemoteMM: Load complete
    RemoteMM-->>Engine: Scaling complete
